//! Polena standard library package entry point.
//!
//! Standard-library modules are imported by path, for example `@std/core`,
//! `@std/io`, `@std/option`, `@std/result`, `@std/parse`, `@std/math`,
//! `@std/string`, `@std/array`, `@std/collections/map`, and
//! `@std/collections/set`. There is no compiler-provided prelude; import names
//! explicitly.
